Class VoterBallots

  • java.lang.Object
    • VoterBallots

  • public class VoterBallots
extends java.lang.Object
    A class that represents a set of voter ballots. It is an array list of Ballots (ballots are an array list of candidates a voter chose)

    I affirm that this program is entirely my own work and none of it is the work of any other person. Created by Alina Lebron on 1/27/15.
